  user_input {
    user_response: "Design a modern futuristic personal portfolio website UI for a Python, AI, and Full Stack Developer with open-source and cybersecurity interests.\n\nTheme:\nDark black space-inspired background with subtle animated stars and tiny particles. Minimal, professional, futuristic, and clean. Avoid gamer RGB style and avoid excessive cyberpunk effects.\n\nVisual Style:\n\n* GitHub + Linux terminal inspired aesthetics\n* Ethical hacker and AI engineer vibe\n* Premium modern SaaS UI\n* Calm intelligent atmosphere\n* Minimal but visually impressive\n\nColor Palette:\n\n* Matte black background (#050505)\n* Neon green accents (#00FF9C)\n* Deep green secondary glow (#00C97B)\n* Small red accent highlights (#FF3B3B)\n* Soft white typography (#EDEDED)\n* Muted gray secondary text (#888888)\n\nHero Section:\n\n* Large round profile picture centered or slightly left aligned\n* Subtle glowing green ring around profile image\n* Name: \342\200\234Shanmugaraj\342\200\235\n* Subtitle: \342\200\234Python \342\200\242 AI \342\200\242 Full Stack Developer\342\200\235\n* Short tagline:\n  \342\200\234Building intelligent and secure software systems.\342\200\235\n\nAdd terminal-style animated typing effect:\n\n> Super_User_Do\n> Learning systems deeply...\n> Building ethical AI systems...\n\nTypography:\n\n* JetBrains Mono for headings\n* Inter font for body text\n* Clean spacing and modern layout\n\nSections:\n\n1. Hero section\n2. About Me\n3. Skills\n4. Projects\n5. Open Source / Security Philosophy\n6. Contact\n\nSkills UI:\nUse terminal/grid styled cards with glowing hover effects.\nInclude:\nPython, FastAPI, React, Docker, LLMs, RAG, Supabase, WebSockets, AI, GitHub\n\nProjects Section:\nModern glassmorphism dark cards with GitHub-style layout.\nAdd subtle hover animations and terminal preview aesthetic.\n\nBackground Effects:\n\n* Slow moving stars\n* Soft grid overlay\n* Minimal glow\n* Blurred gradient lighting\n* Smooth scroll animations\n\nButtons:\nRounded modern buttons with green glow hover effect.\n\nNavbar:\nMinimal transparent navbar with blur effect.\n\nOverall Feel:\nShould look like a real portfolio of an open-source AI engineer who likes Linux, secure systems, and modern developer tools.\n\nImportant:\n\n* Keep design professional and recruiter friendly\n* Avoid skulls, anonymous masks, matrix rain, hacking clich\303\251s\n* No aggressive hacker visuals\n* Focus on ethical engineering and intelligent systems\n\nStyle inspiration:\nGitHub dark UI, Vercel, modern AI startups, Linux terminal aesthetics, cybersecurity dashboard minimalism.\n\nCreate high-quality modern UI mockup with desktop responsive layout.\n"
    items {
      text: "Design a modern futuristic personal portfolio website UI for a Python, AI, and Full Stack Developer with open-source and cybersecurity interests.\n\nTheme:\nDark black space-inspired background with subtle animated stars and tiny particles. Minimal, professional, futuristic, and clean. Avoid gamer RGB style and avoid excessive cyberpunk effects.\n\nVisual Style:\n\n* GitHub + Linux terminal inspired aesthetics\n* Ethical hacker and AI engineer vibe\n* Premium modern SaaS UI\n* Calm intelligent atmosphere\n* Minimal but visually impressive\n\nColor Palette:\n\n* Matte black background (#050505)\n* Neon green accents (#00FF9C)\n* Deep green secondary glow (#00C97B)\n* Small red accent highlights (#FF3B3B)\n* Soft white typography (#EDEDED)\n* Muted gray secondary text (#888888)\n\nHero Section:\n\n* Large round profile picture centered or slightly left aligned\n* Subtle glowing green ring around profile image\n* Name: \342\200\234Shanmugaraj\342\200\235\n* Subtitle: \342\200\234Python \342\200\242 AI \342\200\242 Full Stack Developer\342\200\235\n* Short tagline:\n  \342\200\234Building intelligent and secure software systems.\342\200\235\n\nAdd terminal-style animated typing effect:\n\n> Super_User_Do\n> Learning systems deeply...\n> Building ethical AI systems...\n\nTypography:\n\n* JetBrains Mono for headings\n* Inter font for body text\n* Clean spacing and modern layout\n\nSections:\n\n1. Hero section\n2. About Me\n3. Skills\n4. Projects\n5. Open Source / Security Philosophy\n6. Contact\n\nSkills UI:\nUse terminal/grid styled cards with glowing hover effects.\nInclude:\nPython, FastAPI, React, Docker, LLMs, RAG, Supabase, WebSockets, AI, GitHub\n\nProjects Section:\nModern glassmorphism dark cards with GitHub-style layout.\nAdd subtle hover animations and terminal preview aesthetic.\n\nBackground Effects:\n\n* Slow moving stars\n* Soft grid overlay\n* Minimal glow\n* Blurred gradient lighting\n* Smooth scroll animations\n\nButtons:\nRounded modern buttons with green glow hover effect.\n\nNavbar:\nMinimal transparent navbar with blur effect.\n\nOverall Feel:\nShould look like a real portfolio of an open-source AI engineer who likes Linux, secure systems, and modern developer tools.\n\nImportant:\n\n* Keep design professional and recruiter friendly\n* Avoid skulls, anonymous masks, matrix rain, hacking clich\303\251s\n* No aggressive hacker visuals\n* Focus on ethical engineering and intelligent systems\n\nStyle inspiration:\nGitHub dark UI, Vercel, modern AI startups, Linux terminal aesthetics, cybersecurity dashboard minimalism.\n\nCreate high-quality modern UI mockup with desktop responsive layout.\n"
    }
  }
}
