  user_input {
    user_response: "Apply the \"Immersive UI\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Immersive UI\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#050505] text-[#EDEDED] font-sans flex flex-col overflow-hidden relative\\\">\\n  <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"absolute top-[-10%] left-[-10%] w-[40%] h-[40%] bg-[#00C97B] opacity-10 rounded-full blur-[120px]\\\"></div>\\n    <div class=\\\"absolute bottom-[-5%] right-[-5%] w-[30%] h-[30%] bg-[#00FF9C] opacity-5 rounded-full blur-[100px]\\\"></div>\\n    <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 opacity-[0.03]\\\" style=\\\"background-image: radial-gradient(#EDEDED 0.5px, transparent 0.5px); background-size: 24px 24px;\\\"></div>\\n  </div>\\n\\n  <nav class=\\\"h-16 flex items-center justify-between px-10 border-b border-[#EDEDED]/5 bg-[#050505]/50 backdrop-blur-md relative z-10\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-2\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"w-3 h-3 bg-[#00FF9C] rounded-full shadow-[0_0_8px_#00FF9C]\\\"></div>\\n      <span class=\\\"font-mono text-sm tracking-widest text-[#00FF9C]\\\">PORTFOLIO.SH</span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-8 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-medium text-[#888888]\\\">\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-[#00FF9C]\\\">About</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-[#00FF9C]\\\">Stack</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-[#00FF9C]\\\">Projects</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"hover:text-[#00FF9C]\\\">Security</a>\\n      <a href=\\\"#\\\" class=\\\"px-4 py-2 border border-[#00FF9C]/30 rounded-full text-[#00FF9C] hover:bg-[#00FF9C]/10\\\">Contact</a>\\n    </div>\\n  </nav>\\n\\n  <main class=\\\"flex-1 p-8 grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 relative z-10\\\">\\n    <section class=\\\"col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-center space-y-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-8\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"relative\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 bg-[#00FF9C] rounded-full blur-xl opacity-20\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-32 h-32 rounded-full border-2 border-[#00FF9C] p-1 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(0,255,156,0.3)] relative\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-full h-full rounded-full bg-[#1a1a1a] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden\\\">\\n               <div class=\\\"w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-br from-[#00FF9C]/20 to-[#050505]\\\"></div>\\n               <span class=\\\"absolute text-3xl font-mono opacity-50\\\">SR</span>\\n            </div>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n        <div>\\n          <h1 class=\\\"text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-2\\\" style=\\\"font-family: \'Courier New\', monospace;\\\">Shanmugaraj</h1>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xl text-[#00FF9C] font-mono\\\">Python \342\200\242 AI \342\200\242 Full Stack Developer</p>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-[#888888] mt-3 max-w-md text-sm leading-relaxed\\\">Building intelligent and secure software systems with a focus on ethical AI and robust infrastructure.</p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"bg-[#0A0A0A] border border-[#EDEDED]/10 rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-2xl\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"bg-[#151515] px-4 py-2 flex items-center space-x-2 border-b border-[#EDEDED]/5\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#FF3B3B]\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#FFB84D]\\\"></div>\\n          <div class=\\\"w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-[#00C97B]\\\"></div>\\n          <span class=\\\"ml-4 font-mono text-[10px] text-[#888888] tracking-widest uppercase\\\">terminal\342\200\224zsh</span>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"p-6 font-mono text-sm space-y-2 leading-relaxed\\\">\\n          <p><span class=\\\"text-[#00FF9C]\\\">\342\236\234</span> <span class=\\\"text-[#888888]\\\">~</span> Super_User_Do</p>\\n          <p><span class=\\\"text-blue-400 font-bold\\\">[SYSTEM]</span> Learning systems deeply...</p>\\n          <p><span class=\\\"text-blue-400 font-bold\\\">[SYSTEM]</span> Building ethical AI systems...</p>\\n          <p><span class=\\\"text-blue-400 font-bold\\\">[SYSTEM]</span> Secure nodes initialized.</p>\\n          <p class=\\\"inline-block w-2 h-4 bg-[#00FF9C] animate-pulse align-middle ml-1\\\"></p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n\\n      <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-4\\\">\\n        <div class=\\\"p-4 border border-[#EDEDED]/5 bg-[#080808] rounded-xl\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-[#888888] mb-3 block\\\">Security Philosophy</span>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs text-[#EDEDED] leading-relaxed\\\">\\n            Prioritizing encryption, least privilege, and adversarial testing in every layer of development.\\n          </p>\\n        </div>\\n        <div class=\\\"p-4 border border-[#EDEDED]/5 bg-[#080808] rounded-xl\\\">\\n          <span class=\\\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-[#888888] mb-3 block\\\">Open Source</span>\\n          <p class=\\\"text-xs text-[#EDEDED] leading-relaxed\\\">\\n            Active contributor to privacy-focused tools and AI governance frameworks.\\n          </p>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </section>\\n\\n    <section class=\\\"col-span-5 flex flex-col space-y-6\\\">\\n      <div class=\\\"flex-1 border border-[#EDEDED]/10 bg-[#080808] rounded-2xl p-6 relative\\\">\\n        <h3 class=\\\"font-mono text-xs text-[#00FF9C] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6\\\">Top Skills</h3>\\n        <div class=\\\"grid grid-cols-2 gap-3\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-3 p-3 bg-[#0A0A0A] border border-[#EDEDED]/5 rounded-lg group hover:border-[#00FF9C]/30\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#00FF9C]\\\"></div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-mono\\\">Python (FastAPI)</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-3 p-3 bg-[#0A0A0A] border border-[#EDEDED]/5 rounded-lg group hover:border-[#00FF9C]/30\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#00FF9C]\\\"></div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-mono\\\">LLMs / RAG</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-3 p-3 bg-[#0A0A0A] border border-[#EDEDED]/5 rounded-lg group hover:border-[#00FF9C]/30\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#00FF9C]\\\"></div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-mono\\\">React / Next.js</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-3 p-3 bg-[#0A0A0A] border border-[#EDEDED]/5 rounded-lg group hover:border-[#00FF9C]/30\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#00FF9C]\\\"></div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-mono\\\">Docker / Infra</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-3 p-3 bg-[#0A0A0A] border border-[#EDEDED]/5 rounded-lg group hover:border-[#00FF9C]/30\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#00FF9C]\\\"></div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-mono\\\">Supabase</span>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"flex items-center space-x-3 p-3 bg-[#0A0A0A] border border-[#EDEDED]/5 rounded-lg group hover:border-[#00FF9C]/30\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#00FF9C]\\\"></div>\\n            <span class=\\\"text-xs font-mono\\\">WebSockets</span>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n\\n        <h3 class=\\\"font-mono text-xs text-[#00FF9C] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mt-10 mb-6\\\">Featured Projects</h3>\\n        <div class=\\\"space-y-4\\\">\\n          <div class=\\\"p-4 bg-[#050505] border border-[#EDEDED]/10 rounded-lg hover:border-[#00FF9C]/50 transition-colors cursor-default group\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-[#EDEDED] group-hover:text-[#00FF9C]\\\">NeuralSentinel.ai</span>\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#888888] font-mono\\\">Python \342\200\242 PyTorch</span>\\n            </div>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#888888] mt-2\\\">Real-time anomaly detection for distributed server clusters using LSTM.</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"p-4 bg-[#050505] border border-[#EDEDED]/10 rounded-lg hover:border-[#00FF9C]/50 transition-colors cursor-default group\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-[#EDEDED] group-hover:text-[#00FF9C]\\\">HyperScale-API</span>\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#888888] font-mono\\\">FastAPI \342\200\242 Redis</span>\\n            </div>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#888888] mt-2\\\">A high-performance asynchronous microservice for WebSocket streaming.</p>\\n          </div>\\n          <div class=\\\"p-4 bg-[#050505] border border-[#EDEDED]/10 rounded-lg hover:border-[#00FF9C]/50 transition-colors cursor-default group\\\">\\n            <div class=\\\"flex justify-between items-start\\\">\\n              <span class=\\\"text-sm font-bold text-[#EDEDED] group-hover:text-[#00FF9C]\\\">Ethical-Scanner-OS</span>\\n              <span class=\\\"text-[10px] text-[#888888] font-mono\\\">Go \342\200\242 Docker</span>\\n            </div>\\n            <p class=\\\"text-[11px] text-[#888888] mt-2\\\">Open-source automated penetration testing suite for containerized apps.</p>\\n          </div>\\n        </div>\\n      </div>\\n    </section>\\n  </main>\\n\\n  <footer class=\\\"h-12 border-t border-[#EDEDED]/5 px-10 flex items-center justify-between text-[10px] font-mono text-[#888888] uppercase tracking-widest bg-[#050505] relative z-20\\\">\\n    <div class=\\\"flex space-x-6\\\">\\n      <span>Github: <span class=\\\"text-[#EDEDED]\\\">@shanmugaraj</span></span>\\n      <span>Status: <span class=\\\"text-[#00FF9C]\\\">Available for projects</span></span>\\n    </div>\\n    <div>\\n      <span>Built with React & Python Logic</span>\\n    </div>\\n  </footer>\\n</div>\\n                    </body>\\n                  </html>\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_END]"
    items {
      text: "Apply the \"Immersive UI\" design theme to the app.\n[AIS_METADATA_SECTION_START]\nDesign name: Immersive UI\nDesign instructions: Extract ONLY the styling (colors, fonts, spacing, borders, shadows, backgrounds, gradients) and layout patterns (flexbox/grid structure, component arrangement) from the Design HTML below. Do NOT replace or restructure the existing app\'s HTML elements \342\200\224 preserve all existing components, content, and functionality. Only modify CSS/styling and adjust layout containers as needed to match the theme\'s aesthetic.\nDesign HTML:                   <!doctype html>\\n                  <html style=\\\"height: 100%; margin: 0;\\\">\\n                    <head>\\n                      <meta charset=\\\"UTF-8\\\" />\\n                      <meta name=\\\"viewport\\\" content=\\\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\\\" />\\n                      <script src=\\\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4\\\"></script>\\n                      <link href=\\\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@20..48,100..700,0..1,-50..200\\\" rel=\\\"stylesheet\\\" />\\n                      <style>\\n                        body { margin: 0; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; overflow: hidden; }\\n                        /* Fallback classes in case Tailwind fails to load in sandbox */\\n                        .h-full { height: 100%; }\\n                        .w-full { width: 100%; }\\n                        .flex { display: flex; }\\n                        .flex-col { flex-direction: column; }\\n                        .flex-1 { flex: 1 1 0%; }\\n                      </style>\\n                    </head>\\n                    <body>\\n                      <div class=\\\"w-[1024px] h-[768px] bg-[#050505] text-[#EDEDED] font-sans flex flex-col overflow-hidden relative\\\">\\n  <div class=\\\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none overflow-hidden\\\">\\n    <div cl